oku. == See Also == * {{ill|Yamato Eikyō no Ran|ja|大和永享の乱|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Eikyō no Ran|qq=|1=Yamato Eikyō War|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11433497}} * [[:en:Warrior monk|Warrior Monk]]
